1
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,348
Mom...

2
00:01:10,149 --> 00:01:12,819
What do we do...

3
00:01:13,452 --> 00:01:15,288
I'm not feeling too good.

4
00:01:16,556 --> 00:01:17,757
You're not feeling too good?

5
00:01:19,659 --> 00:01:20,493
No.

6
00:01:25,464 --> 00:01:26,799
Did you write the last letter?

7
00:01:32,538 --> 00:01:37,577
(Han Gyeol has written a letter
for someone with a heavy heart.)

8
00:01:37,944 --> 00:01:40,045
I don't think this is a good sign.

9
00:01:40,046 --> 00:01:43,215
I noticed that he kept looking at things
very realistically.

10
00:01:43,216 --> 00:01:45,450
Yeah. I agree.

11
00:01:45,451 --> 00:01:49,521
He's torn between the reality
and what his mind's telling him.

12
00:01:49,522 --> 00:01:51,690
Yes, between reality and his ideals.

13
00:01:51,691 --> 00:01:54,025
In the end, I think he's made a decision,

14
00:01:54,026 --> 00:01:55,495
so that's what the tears are for.

15
00:01:57,997 --> 00:02:02,134
(Han Gyeol steps out
to deliver his letter right away.)

16
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:10,542
(He's headed to Eun Na Rae's room.)

17
00:02:10,543 --> 00:02:11,611
For Eun Na Rae.

18
00:02:12,778 --> 00:02:13,713
Did you have a good night's sleep?

19
00:02:13,714 --> 00:02:15,081
Yeah, good morning.

20
00:02:16,115 --> 00:02:19,618
I have something I want to give...

21
00:02:19,619 --> 00:02:21,086
To show my thanks.

22
00:02:21,087 --> 00:02:22,555
You didn't need to.

23
00:02:23,289 --> 00:02:24,589
No, you don't need to do this.

24
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,491
No, it's really nothing. It's nothing big.

25
00:02:26,492 --> 00:02:27,393
Thank you.

26
00:02:29,862 --> 00:02:32,732
You don't need to read it here.
Just when you have time...

27
00:02:33,966 --> 00:02:35,268
The thing is, Eun Na Rae...

28
00:02:36,469 --> 00:02:38,336
likes you, Han Gyeol,

29
00:02:38,337 --> 00:02:40,405
but she was worried about something.

30
00:02:40,406 --> 00:02:41,606
Right, both of them...

31
00:02:41,607 --> 00:02:44,543
- Now that today's the final decision day,
- They each have their worries.

32
00:02:44,544 --> 00:02:47,746
the way I look at it, it's 80:20.

33
00:02:47,747 --> 00:02:51,516
That 20% is what's holding her back.

34
00:02:51,517 --> 00:02:53,186
(There's 20% of hesitation left.)

35
00:02:54,854 --> 00:02:58,356
We should both just go with
what we think is best.

36
00:02:58,357 --> 00:02:59,624
You think so?

37
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:04,363
Even yesterday, I knew she had things
to consider about me as well.

38
00:03:04,997 --> 00:03:07,365
I wasn't affected,

39
00:03:07,366 --> 00:03:08,367
but,

40
00:03:08,734 --> 00:03:10,902
we're about to make the final decision
and there are more things to consider?

41
00:03:10,903 --> 00:03:12,504
That's what I thought,

42
00:03:12,505 --> 00:03:14,240
and it made me anxious.

43
00:03:18,344 --> 00:03:22,481
(Cho Eun Na Rae and her mother
read the letter right away.)

44
00:03:22,482 --> 00:03:23,549
What does it say?

45
00:03:23,916 --> 00:03:25,183
It made me really happy.

46
00:03:25,184 --> 00:03:30,523
He had written the sweetest,
most thoughtful letter.

47
00:03:31,958 --> 00:03:34,259
He wrote that

48
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:39,531
the more he got to know me,
he thought I was a shining jewel...

49
00:03:39,532 --> 00:03:41,132
who's hard to come across.

50
00:03:41,133 --> 00:03:43,368
And if there was ever anyone...

51
00:03:43,369 --> 00:03:46,939
He said that if anyone
questioned my worth,

52
00:03:47,473 --> 00:03:50,409
he would defend me to the end.

53
00:03:53,346 --> 00:03:54,547
It was...

54
00:03:57,350 --> 00:03:58,317
I felt...

55
00:03:59,352 --> 00:04:00,887
A part of me felt bad.

56
00:04:04,657 --> 00:04:05,625
That's how...

57
00:04:07,693 --> 00:04:10,563
I was able to look back on myself,

58
00:04:11,297 --> 00:04:13,666
and I was very touched by his sincerity.

59
00:04:15,268 --> 00:04:19,338
(In the end, what choice will they make?)

60
00:04:20,673 --> 00:04:21,907
Hey, Myo Jin.

61
00:04:21,908 --> 00:04:24,143
(Myo Jin is here to talk to Se Hoon.)

62
00:04:24,577 --> 00:04:25,710
What time did you sleep?

63
00:04:25,711 --> 00:04:27,680
Yesterday?
I went to bed around three or four.

64
00:04:29,715 --> 00:04:33,552
I actually wanted
to talk to you yesterday,

65
00:04:33,553 --> 00:04:35,320
but you had already gone to bed.

66
00:04:35,321 --> 00:04:36,556
Really?

67
00:04:41,994 --> 00:04:45,364
Why don't you ever come talk to me?
Are you not curious about me?

68
00:04:46,132 --> 00:04:47,666
- To you?
- Yeah.

69
00:04:47,667 --> 00:04:50,269
There was time this morning too,

70
00:04:51,037 --> 00:04:53,072
so I was kind of sad about it.

71
00:04:55,975 --> 00:04:57,543
Yesterday? Yesterday...

72
00:04:58,411 --> 00:05:01,179
No, not like that.
Be more confident about it.

73
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:03,048
I missed you so much,

74
00:05:03,049 --> 00:05:04,884
but every time I went to see you,

75
00:05:05,852 --> 00:05:07,587
there were too many obstacles.

76
00:05:10,289 --> 00:05:13,125
So that's why you need to be more...

77
00:05:13,726 --> 00:05:15,361
You need to be more expressive.

78
00:05:16,195 --> 00:05:18,930
That's how a girl's going to know
how you feel.

79
00:05:18,931 --> 00:05:19,832
Right?

80
00:05:20,466 --> 00:05:23,436
I was kind of puzzled the whole time.

81
00:05:25,171 --> 00:05:26,339
Then do you...

82
00:05:28,975 --> 00:05:32,378
Are you open to getting married
in the near future?

83
00:05:34,247 --> 00:05:36,047
For me...

84
00:05:36,048 --> 00:05:39,385
I would like to get married next year.

85
00:05:40,353 --> 00:05:41,821
Throughout our conversations...

86
00:05:43,122 --> 00:05:46,825
I think I got the sense
that you weren't really interested...

87
00:05:46,826 --> 00:05:48,427
in dating or marriage.

88
00:05:50,029 --> 00:05:54,267
So, maybe I thought
it's because you're not really...

89
00:05:55,101 --> 00:05:57,002
I wouldn't say not interested, but...

90
00:05:57,003 --> 00:06:00,438
No, I'm interested in you,

91
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,774
but I'm also...

92
00:06:02,708 --> 00:06:03,909
How should I say this?

93
00:06:03,910 --> 00:06:05,777
I'm not sure about how I feel yet,

94
00:06:05,778 --> 00:06:09,382
so it was hard for me
to go all out like that.

95
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:12,984
You must've had
a lot of serious conversations then.

96
00:06:12,985 --> 00:06:16,688
With other people,
it must've been more serious.

97
00:06:16,689 --> 00:06:18,890
Right. We were on the same page,

98
00:06:18,891 --> 00:06:22,028
and everything was very precise
with anything we talked about.

99
00:06:24,030 --> 00:06:25,630
That's how it was.

100
00:06:25,631 --> 00:06:26,499
Right.

101
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:30,069
That's why I feel so conflicted.

102
00:06:31,103 --> 00:06:33,806
Normally, my mind should've leaned
towards that person...

103
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:37,210
after those serious conversations,

104
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:40,613
but I'm still thinking about you.

105
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,248
That's why I missed you.

106
00:06:43,249 --> 00:06:45,918
Whenever I tried to start a conversation
like that with you,

107
00:06:46,452 --> 00:06:48,286
you seemed very awkward.

108
00:06:48,287 --> 00:06:49,354
Really?

109
00:06:49,355 --> 00:06:50,622
It did feel a little awkward.

110
00:06:50,623 --> 00:06:52,290
That made me think as well.

111
00:06:52,291 --> 00:06:57,295
Is he not that serious about me?
Is his feeling not that big?

112
00:06:57,296 --> 00:06:59,831
Is that why he's not very expressive?

113
00:06:59,832 --> 00:07:01,299
Those kinds of thoughts.

114
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:04,070
It wasn't because I wasn't interested.

115
00:07:05,738 --> 00:07:08,140
I told you yesterday.

116
00:07:08,141 --> 00:07:11,711
I can already see it.
I see us going on dates,

117
00:07:12,378 --> 00:07:15,982
and spending time together
outside of this.

118
00:07:16,616 --> 00:07:18,316
It's so clear to me.

119
00:07:18,317 --> 00:07:19,485
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

120
00:07:31,164 --> 00:07:32,264
How...

121
00:07:32,265 --> 00:07:33,099
Yeah?

122
00:07:36,302 --> 00:07:37,736
How do I seem right now?

123
00:07:37,737 --> 00:07:39,371
What? You?

124
00:07:39,372 --> 00:07:41,239
- How do I seem?
- You?

125
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,641
Why? Why is he asking that?

126
00:07:42,642 --> 00:07:44,110
Why is he asking how he seems?

127
00:07:45,211 --> 00:07:49,549
You look... You look good. Yeah.

128
00:07:50,483 --> 00:07:51,350
Why?

129
00:07:52,418 --> 00:07:53,219
Why?

130
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,387
It was...

131
00:07:56,289 --> 00:07:57,756
just an excuse.

132
00:07:57,757 --> 00:07:59,025
I wanted to see you like this.

133
00:08:00,126 --> 00:08:01,159
They're...

134
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,128
Wait a minute.

135
00:08:03,496 --> 00:08:04,664
You've got to be kidding me.

136
00:08:06,232 --> 00:08:07,166
Why are they...

137
00:08:07,967 --> 00:08:11,336
The thing is...

138
00:08:11,337 --> 00:08:14,005
They keep saying it's 50:50,

139
00:08:14,006 --> 00:08:18,311
but it's been settled already,
like two days ago.

140
00:08:18,878 --> 00:08:20,212
I literally drooled twice because of him.

141
00:08:20,213 --> 00:08:21,481
Seriously?

142
00:08:23,449 --> 00:08:24,317
Why?

143
00:08:24,318 --> 00:08:25,318
It was...

144
00:08:27,353 --> 00:08:28,787
just an excuse.

145
00:08:28,788 --> 00:08:30,122
I wanted to see you like this.

146
00:08:31,591 --> 00:08:33,626
I feel like I have to look away now.

147
00:08:37,029 --> 00:08:38,163
She's shy.

148
00:08:38,164 --> 00:08:40,265
Of course.

149
00:08:40,266 --> 00:08:41,600
Excuse me, sir.

150
00:08:41,601 --> 00:08:44,303
You're staring so hard right now.
It's too intense, sir.

151
00:08:44,971 --> 00:08:49,108
This is the only time I've got,
so I need to make the most of this time.

152
00:08:51,711 --> 00:08:53,245
This intensely?

153
00:08:53,246 --> 00:08:54,647
It's weird.

154
00:08:55,481 --> 00:08:57,817
They're going to kiss or something.

155
00:08:59,719 --> 00:09:00,686
You seem cold right now.

156
00:09:03,656 --> 00:09:04,624
Isn't it pretty?

157
00:09:04,624 --> 00:09:05,558
Yeah, it's pretty.

158
00:09:06,025 --> 00:09:07,392
Yeah, it's pretty.

159
00:09:07,393 --> 00:09:09,462
Do I need to take my jacket off for you?

160
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:13,598
The weather's all over the place here.

161
00:09:13,599 --> 00:09:16,469
The temperature swings are huge, you know.

162
00:09:17,136 --> 00:09:19,572
- That makes it feel colder.
- Thank you.

163
00:09:20,373 --> 00:09:21,274
Thanks.

164
00:09:21,275 --> 00:09:22,742
- You look good in it.
- Yeah?

165
00:09:25,444 --> 00:09:30,817
In the end,
I think my mind is pointing to you.

166
00:09:32,718 --> 00:09:34,986
- Same here.
- Really?

167
00:09:34,987 --> 00:09:38,223
My mind is pointing to you.

168
00:09:38,224 --> 00:09:40,860
- My mind is telling me it's you.
- You know, though, right?

169
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:44,197
My mind is telling me it's you,

170
00:09:44,964 --> 00:09:45,898
but...

171
00:09:45,899 --> 00:09:47,567
(Se Hoon and Myo Jin are busy
learning about how they feel.)

172
00:09:49,368 --> 00:09:53,673
(Then, an alarm rings.)

173
00:09:53,873 --> 00:09:56,576
Today is the day of the final decision.

174
00:09:57,276 --> 00:10:01,247
Before the final decision,
here's an important announcement.

175
00:10:01,514 --> 00:10:04,182
The sons and daughters
will make the decisions first,

176
00:10:04,183 --> 00:10:08,553
but both mothers have to agree
to the decision...

177
00:10:08,554 --> 00:10:10,356
for them to become the final couple.

178
00:10:11,123 --> 00:10:12,157
Seriously?

179
00:10:12,158 --> 00:10:13,659
My goodness gracious.

180
00:10:14,293 --> 00:10:16,529
(Just laughs)

181
00:10:16,963 --> 00:10:19,732
Okay, that's fine by me.

182
00:10:21,701 --> 00:10:24,769
- Really?
- That's right.

183
00:10:24,770 --> 00:10:25,671
Seriously?

184
00:10:25,672 --> 00:10:28,640
For the final decision,

185
00:10:28,641 --> 00:10:31,710
even if a son and a daughter
choose each other,

186
00:10:31,711 --> 00:10:35,647
both mothers have to agree
to the decision...

187
00:10:35,648 --> 00:10:37,549
for them to be a final couple.

188
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:39,451
If one of them decides against it,

189
00:10:39,452 --> 00:10:42,754
they can't end up as a final couple.

190
00:10:42,755 --> 00:10:44,990
That means both mothers have to agree
to the decision?

191
00:10:44,991 --> 00:10:45,892
Yes.

192
00:10:45,893 --> 00:10:47,325
Really?

193
00:10:47,326 --> 00:10:50,095
This is going to be hard then.

194
00:10:50,096 --> 00:10:51,931
If someone goes against the decision,

195
00:10:52,698 --> 00:10:54,400
things are going to be awkward
when they get home.

196
00:10:55,001 --> 00:10:58,136
Mothers, please choose the person...

197
00:10:58,137 --> 00:11:02,041
you'd like to talk to for the last time,
excluding your child.

198
00:11:03,276 --> 00:11:04,777
Why do we get to do the tough part?

199
00:11:07,814 --> 00:11:09,715
This is the final showdown.

200
00:11:10,583 --> 00:11:11,584
The final meeting.

201
00:11:13,352 --> 00:11:17,089
(This talk could be the last opportunity
before the final decision.)

202
00:11:18,457 --> 00:11:21,360
(Who will the mothers choose?)

203
00:11:21,994 --> 00:11:26,933
(The mothers wait for their choices.)

204
00:11:28,601 --> 00:11:29,535
Gosh...

205
00:11:32,071 --> 00:11:36,008
(Who's Jin Joo's mother waiting for?)

206
00:11:37,243 --> 00:11:38,144
Welcome.

207
00:11:39,479 --> 00:11:41,813
(The final meeting
Kim Jin Joo's mother and Jang Min Cheol)

208
00:11:41,814 --> 00:11:42,815
Ma'am, please.

209
00:11:46,552 --> 00:11:48,421
I feel like...

210
00:11:49,388 --> 00:11:51,691
I wasn't able to see you properly.

211
00:11:52,225 --> 00:11:53,459
Same here, ma'am.

212
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:57,930
I've been unable to visit you
as often as I should.

213
00:11:58,965 --> 00:11:59,799
How was...

214
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,800
Yes.

215
00:12:00,801 --> 00:12:02,068
the date with Jin Joo?

216
00:12:02,435 --> 00:12:04,803
I heard you two went on dates
while I wasn't here.

217
00:12:04,804 --> 00:12:05,671
Yes, ma'am.

218
00:12:06,339 --> 00:12:08,341
I went to see her a few times.

219
00:12:08,908 --> 00:12:09,909
How was it?

220
00:12:10,610 --> 00:12:12,845
Jin Joo seemed like a very honest person,

221
00:12:14,013 --> 00:12:15,414
and I realized...

222
00:12:16,149 --> 00:12:19,385
that I'm drawn to someone like that.

223
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,387
I also...

224
00:12:22,388 --> 00:12:24,991
I also don't like pretending
to be someone you're not.

225
00:12:25,858 --> 00:12:27,026
I don't like hiding myself.

226
00:12:28,194 --> 00:12:31,630
Then, her personality was okay...

227
00:12:31,631 --> 00:12:34,065
You didn't fight with her, right?

228
00:12:34,066 --> 00:12:35,134
No, we didn't.

229
00:12:36,502 --> 00:12:39,438
I like those things about her,

230
00:12:40,907 --> 00:12:42,074
and I find it cute.

231
00:12:42,408 --> 00:12:46,212
I'm glad you even like those things...

232
00:12:48,014 --> 00:12:49,048
about her.

233
00:12:50,716 --> 00:12:55,654
How does your mother think about her?
Does she like her?

234
00:12:55,655 --> 00:12:57,556
I heard she went to see her yesterday.

235
00:12:57,557 --> 00:12:58,457
That's right.

236
00:12:58,691 --> 00:13:00,393
All the mothers went out yesterday,

237
00:13:00,793 --> 00:13:03,262
and we talked for the first time
when she got back.

238
00:13:03,996 --> 00:13:05,064
I wanted to know how my mother felt.

239
00:13:06,899 --> 00:13:11,036
I asked her for her top pick
at the moment...

240
00:13:11,037 --> 00:13:12,171
to keep in consideration.

241
00:13:12,538 --> 00:13:14,340
That's when she said it was Jin Joo.

242
00:13:15,274 --> 00:13:19,512
Who are you leaning towards more?

243
00:13:20,947 --> 00:13:22,180
Then?

244
00:13:22,181 --> 00:13:23,149
Jin Joo.

245
00:13:24,317 --> 00:13:25,218
It's changed.

246
00:13:26,052 --> 00:13:28,220
That's what she said,
so she's definitely...

247
00:13:28,221 --> 00:13:29,222
How thankful.

248
00:13:30,456 --> 00:13:31,890
- I'm glad.
- Not at all, ma'am.

249
00:13:31,891 --> 00:13:33,259
I should be the one who's thankful.

250
00:13:34,861 --> 00:13:36,495
I'll be rooting for you two.

251
00:13:36,496 --> 00:13:37,597
Thank you, ma'am.

252
00:13:38,564 --> 00:13:39,998
I'll try my best not to disappoint you.

253
00:13:39,999 --> 00:13:41,100
Yes, thank you.

254
00:13:42,635 --> 00:13:45,470
First of all,
it felt comfortable talking to him.

255
00:13:45,471 --> 00:13:48,306
He seemed way more mature than Jin Joo.

256
00:13:48,307 --> 00:13:50,709
I wanted someone who could understand,

257
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:52,177
or someone...

258
00:13:52,178 --> 00:13:56,516
who could lead her in the right direction.

259
00:13:57,150 --> 00:14:00,453
I think he's someone who could
lead her in the right direction.

260
00:14:02,021 --> 00:14:04,523
(The final meeting
Kim Hyun Jin's mother and Jang Min Cheol)

261
00:14:04,524 --> 00:14:06,024
How did you sleep last night?

262
00:14:06,025 --> 00:14:07,326
It was a bit...

263
00:14:07,894 --> 00:14:08,661
You didn't sleep well.

264
00:14:08,662 --> 00:14:10,162
No, I couldn't but...

265
00:14:10,163 --> 00:14:13,299
Min Cheol seems uncomfortable.

266
00:14:14,467 --> 00:14:17,170
It's so awkward.

267
00:14:17,603 --> 00:14:22,440
I'd like to know
how you feel about Hyun Jin.

268
00:14:22,441 --> 00:14:25,677
All four of us went on that date together,
but you still...

269
00:14:25,678 --> 00:14:28,881
had Jin Joo on your mind,
so you two ended up going on a date.

270
00:14:30,516 --> 00:14:32,118
It made be curious about your feelings.

271
00:14:33,052 --> 00:14:35,420
This is such a hard thing to say
to her mother.

272
00:14:35,421 --> 00:14:36,454
Right.

273
00:14:36,455 --> 00:14:37,890
This is tough.

274
00:14:41,828 --> 00:14:45,998
Actually, I've been meaning
to talk to Hyun Jin first,

275
00:14:46,432 --> 00:14:49,902
and to you too, ma'am, about my feelings
and what's on my mind.

276
00:14:50,636 --> 00:14:53,672
But it was too late yesterday, so...

277
00:14:53,673 --> 00:14:57,043
I think it's important
that I say this today.

278
00:14:57,977 --> 00:14:59,812
First of all, Hyun Jin...

279
00:15:02,381 --> 00:15:04,283
Hyun Jin is an amazing person, but...

280
00:15:06,052 --> 00:15:07,285
I mean,

281
00:15:07,286 --> 00:15:08,620
I could be making excuses,

282
00:15:08,621 --> 00:15:10,722
but I feel like she'd be fine...

283
00:15:10,723 --> 00:15:12,390
- without me.
- I see.

284
00:15:12,391 --> 00:15:14,359
But I feel like she'd be fine...

285
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:17,162
- without me.
- I see.

286
00:15:17,163 --> 00:15:21,734
It's okay. You can be honest.
Don't feel burdened.

287
00:15:23,336 --> 00:15:25,704
She's an incredible person.

288
00:15:25,705 --> 00:15:26,872
Yes.

289
00:15:26,873 --> 00:15:27,840
Yes, I see.

290
00:15:27,841 --> 00:15:30,742
The other person seemed like
she needed me.

291
00:15:30,743 --> 00:15:32,377
That's what I thought.

292
00:15:32,378 --> 00:15:34,547
No, good for you.

293
00:15:35,681 --> 00:15:37,817
- That's what I wanted to say.
- Yes.

294
00:15:38,050 --> 00:15:42,854
I'd like to apologize
for not telling you this sooner.

295
00:15:42,855 --> 00:15:45,056
No, please don't be.

296
00:15:45,057 --> 00:15:48,326
It's okay.

297
00:15:48,327 --> 00:15:52,164
This isn't her last opportunity
or anything, so...

298
00:15:52,165 --> 00:15:53,366
That's how we feel.

299
00:15:54,467 --> 00:15:56,535
I thought she was amazing,

300
00:15:56,536 --> 00:15:59,838
that she's just an incredible individual.

301
00:15:59,839 --> 00:16:03,008
He admitted that
the other person needed him more,

302
00:16:03,009 --> 00:16:05,877
so there are no hard feelings or anything.

303
00:16:05,878 --> 00:16:08,681
I told him that I support his decision.

304
00:16:09,415 --> 00:16:11,383
On this program, if you want to say no,

305
00:16:11,384 --> 00:16:12,984
you need to say no to the mother too.

306
00:16:12,985 --> 00:16:14,619
That's double the pain.

307
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:16,789
- This is an incredibly tough thing to do.
- It's very tough.

308
00:16:17,490 --> 00:16:20,359
(Hyun Jin's mother is back in her room.)

309
00:16:21,093 --> 00:16:25,297
I'm back. I'm here.

310
00:16:25,298 --> 00:16:26,364
Hello, ma'am.

311
00:16:26,365 --> 00:16:28,967
(Min Cheol is here for Jin Joo.)

312
00:16:28,968 --> 00:16:30,702
Did you have a good talk?

313
00:16:30,703 --> 00:16:32,872
This is the mother's living room.

314
00:16:33,139 --> 00:16:34,240
Say hi.

315
00:16:34,540 --> 00:16:36,175
- Say hi?
- It's the mother's living room.

316
00:16:37,243 --> 00:16:39,378
I'll talk to Jin Joo a bit more, ma'am.

317
00:16:40,847 --> 00:16:42,081
Why?

318
00:16:42,582 --> 00:16:43,883
Why? Am I asking for you too much?

319
00:16:44,884 --> 00:16:46,953
Do you miss me?
Why do you keep calling me?

320
00:16:48,421 --> 00:16:49,355
Is there something?

321
00:16:49,622 --> 00:16:50,556
I called you because I missed you.

322
00:16:50,557 --> 00:16:51,923
Is there something? Why did you call me?

323
00:16:51,924 --> 00:16:53,091
There's nothing.

324
00:16:53,092 --> 00:16:54,093
Why did you call for me?

325
00:16:54,527 --> 00:16:56,895
We couldn't finish our conversation
because I had to go for a meeting.

326
00:16:56,896 --> 00:16:58,597
He just naturally took her purse.

327
00:16:58,598 --> 00:16:59,865
Has he made the choice already?

328
00:16:59,866 --> 00:17:01,700
Was that the final choice?

329
00:17:01,701 --> 00:17:03,001
He'd made the decision already.

330
00:17:03,002 --> 00:17:04,370
I mean, he took her purse for her.

331
00:17:06,305 --> 00:17:11,444
(Han Gyeol's mother
is waiting for someone.)

332
00:17:11,878 --> 00:17:15,481
I wonder who she chose to talk to.

333
00:17:16,015 --> 00:17:18,684
I think there's only one person for this.

334
00:17:20,386 --> 00:17:22,488
(Knocking)

335
00:17:25,791 --> 00:17:28,461
- There can't be anyone else.
- Hello, ma'am.

336
00:17:29,395 --> 00:17:30,495
It's Eun Na Rae.

337
00:17:30,496 --> 00:17:31,563
(The final meeting
Seo Han Gyeol's mother and Cho Eun Na Rae)

338
00:17:31,564 --> 00:17:32,765
It was nice.

339
00:17:33,065 --> 00:17:37,536
We haven't been able
to have a serious conversation like this,

340
00:17:37,537 --> 00:17:40,540
so I felt grateful
to have an opportunity like this.

341
00:17:41,274 --> 00:17:44,075
Thank you for taking the time to see me.

342
00:17:44,076 --> 00:17:46,211
No, not at all.
I wanted to do this before we left.

343
00:17:46,212 --> 00:17:49,247
If it weren't for this,
we wouldn't be having this conversation.

344
00:17:49,248 --> 00:17:51,416
That's why I think
this time is so precious.

345
00:17:51,417 --> 00:17:53,118
I'm happy to have this opportunity
with you.

346
00:17:53,119 --> 00:17:54,287
Yes, of course.

347
00:17:55,188 --> 00:17:57,522
I'm so glad
that your mother likes Han Gyeol.

348
00:17:57,523 --> 00:17:58,723
Of course.

349
00:17:58,724 --> 00:18:01,159
He's such a likable person.

350
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:02,494
No, no.

351
00:18:02,495 --> 00:18:03,962
You're more amazing,

352
00:18:03,963 --> 00:18:06,698
but I haven't been able to express that,

353
00:18:06,699 --> 00:18:08,801
so I wanted to say sorry.

354
00:18:09,902 --> 00:18:12,170
Han Gyeol complimented me a lot.

355
00:18:12,171 --> 00:18:13,271
Did he?

356
00:18:13,272 --> 00:18:15,474
And before anything else,

357
00:18:15,475 --> 00:18:20,045
I wanted to say that I'm truly grateful.

358
00:18:20,046 --> 00:18:23,149
How do you feel now?

359
00:18:23,883 --> 00:18:27,753
I want to know
how strong your feelings are.

360
00:18:28,621 --> 00:18:30,856
That night,

361
00:18:30,857 --> 00:18:34,659
after having
that honest conversation with him,

362
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:37,496
my feelings have grown a lot.

363
00:18:37,497 --> 00:18:39,130
It's amazing, really.

364
00:18:39,131 --> 00:18:41,967
My feelings have grown a lot.

365
00:18:41,968 --> 00:18:43,869
It's amazing, really.

366
00:18:43,870 --> 00:18:46,506
I think I'm starting to see him
in a romantic way.

367
00:18:48,174 --> 00:18:49,175
That's why...

368
00:18:50,243 --> 00:18:52,644
The thing that worries me is...

369
00:18:52,645 --> 00:18:54,813
Apart from your feelings,

370
00:18:54,814 --> 00:18:56,982
it's the partial things that we see.

371
00:18:56,983 --> 00:18:58,483
For example, the age gap.

372
00:18:58,484 --> 00:19:01,053
Things like that that can't be controlled.

373
00:19:01,387 --> 00:19:05,023
Han Gyeol also knows
I'm worried about those things.

374
00:19:05,024 --> 00:19:09,961
Han Gyeol is five years younger
than his brother.

375
00:19:09,962 --> 00:19:12,397
I mean, if you dated
someone other than Han Gyeol,

376
00:19:12,398 --> 00:19:14,900
it's something
that wouldn't even be a problem.

377
00:19:14,901 --> 00:19:16,536
It's because it's Han Gyeol.

378
00:19:18,738 --> 00:19:23,042
- She's older than his brother.
- Right.

379
00:19:24,177 --> 00:19:25,178
Of course,

380
00:19:26,913 --> 00:19:28,780
I think that's a very valid concern.

381
00:19:28,781 --> 00:19:30,115
I have absolutely no hard feelings...

382
00:19:30,116 --> 00:19:32,984
about your concerns regarding that.

383
00:19:32,985 --> 00:19:34,786
If I were in your shoes,

384
00:19:34,787 --> 00:19:39,357
I think it's something
I would be concerned about as well.

385
00:19:39,358 --> 00:19:40,326
However,

386
00:19:41,561 --> 00:19:44,529
if we do choose each other,

387
00:19:44,530 --> 00:19:49,202
I'm going to take that
as a sign that everything's fine.

388
00:19:55,107 --> 00:19:56,075
Yes...

389
00:19:56,076 --> 00:19:58,044
Also, one more thing is,

390
00:19:58,478 --> 00:20:02,048
I'm concerned that your mother...

391
00:20:03,983 --> 00:20:09,121
might want to rush into the next step
after the final decision here.

392
00:20:10,189 --> 00:20:16,361
For me, though, I'm not thinking of it
as something that heavy.

393
00:20:16,362 --> 00:20:19,831
I'd like to get to know each other more.

394
00:20:19,832 --> 00:20:23,736
I think that's
what the final decision means for me.

395
00:20:24,537 --> 00:20:27,572
Even for the things
you're concerned about...

396
00:20:27,573 --> 00:20:33,745
I feel like we need to
get to know each other more...

397
00:20:33,746 --> 00:20:39,751
for us to figure out if it's something
we can work with and manage.

398
00:20:39,752 --> 00:20:43,054
I'm not putting too much weight on it.

399
00:20:43,055 --> 00:20:45,323
I think she handled that well.

400
00:20:45,324 --> 00:20:47,425
The mother's expression has lightened up.

401
00:20:47,426 --> 00:20:49,061
- Are you curious about anything else?
- No, no.

402
00:20:51,197 --> 00:20:54,200
Honestly, I felt relieved.

403
00:20:54,367 --> 00:20:57,269
However, it did make me think...

404
00:20:57,270 --> 00:21:00,105
that they might be
on another level with their feelings.

405
00:21:00,106 --> 00:21:06,478
Han Gyeol has only focused on one person
while he was here,

406
00:21:06,479 --> 00:21:09,782
but have those times become too trivial?

407
00:21:10,983 --> 00:21:12,151
Ask me if you're curious.

408
00:21:13,085 --> 00:21:15,254
You two should go inside and talk.

409
00:21:17,557 --> 00:21:20,826
Anyway, for Eun Na Rae,

410
00:21:20,827 --> 00:21:25,263
she's not putting
too much meaning into the choice.

411
00:21:25,264 --> 00:21:26,498
That's what she said?

412
00:21:26,499 --> 00:21:28,701
Just a casual thing.

413
00:21:30,303 --> 00:21:34,774
I'm not sure if she just said that
because it was me.

414
00:21:36,442 --> 00:21:37,310
I see.

415
00:21:41,714 --> 00:21:42,582
Is that so?

416
00:21:46,686 --> 00:21:47,786
That wasn't it.

417
00:21:47,787 --> 00:21:48,721
That wasn't...

418
00:21:48,722 --> 00:21:52,492
I think the meaning got a bit twisted.

419
00:21:52,992 --> 00:21:54,359
Do you have more on your mind now?

420
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:55,261
No, well...

421
00:21:55,962 --> 00:21:56,896
Casual...

422
00:21:57,864 --> 00:22:00,633
So, just casually, to see how it goes?

423
00:22:00,967 --> 00:22:03,236
Yeah, that's what she said.

424
00:22:03,803 --> 00:22:08,841
Nothing big like marriage or anything.
Just casually.

425
00:22:09,208 --> 00:22:10,643
But the thing is,

426
00:22:12,411 --> 00:22:13,812
I'm still concerned...

427
00:22:13,813 --> 00:22:16,516
about age-related pregnancy risks,

428
00:22:17,116 --> 00:22:19,085
the issue of an irregular work schedule,

429
00:22:20,186 --> 00:22:21,853
and the concerns about financial habit.

430
00:22:21,854 --> 00:22:23,856
Those things are still concerning to me.

431
00:22:25,391 --> 00:22:28,827
So, to see each other casually,
to see how it goes...

432
00:22:28,828 --> 00:22:30,930
Other than those, things are already good,

433
00:22:31,564 --> 00:22:34,901
but that's not why I came on this show.

434
00:22:35,501 --> 00:22:36,402
Right.

435
00:22:36,836 --> 00:22:38,304
Honestly, that's not why I'm here.

436
00:22:39,005 --> 00:22:42,675
It's not like she has more time outside.

437
00:22:43,843 --> 00:22:46,279
Then I'm still the one
who has to make the decision.

438
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:49,916
Even if we start seeing each other,

439
00:22:51,284 --> 00:22:53,151
if I decide down the line...

440
00:22:53,152 --> 00:22:54,754
that it's not going to work,

441
00:22:56,055 --> 00:22:57,456
then to her it's...

442
00:22:58,658 --> 00:23:00,358
That's what I keep thinking about.

443
00:23:00,359 --> 00:23:02,028
Then you shouldn't choose her.

444
00:23:02,929 --> 00:23:03,995
That's what you think, right?

445
00:23:03,996 --> 00:23:04,831
Yes.

446
00:23:05,998 --> 00:23:07,066
No way.

447
00:23:09,702 --> 00:23:11,169
His mother is...

448
00:23:11,170 --> 00:23:12,704
(Han Gyeol has so much on his mind
before the final decision.)

449
00:23:12,705 --> 00:23:14,707
His mother keeps...

450
00:23:15,174 --> 00:23:18,010
If he has to make a decision like this,

451
00:23:18,478 --> 00:23:21,480
I don't think he'll choose her.

452
00:23:21,481 --> 00:23:22,948
I think...

453
00:23:22,949 --> 00:23:25,550
Han Gyeol is feeling hurt because...

454
00:23:25,551 --> 00:23:26,885
his mother told him...

455
00:23:26,886 --> 00:23:29,621
that she's just thinking
of something casual...

456
00:23:29,622 --> 00:23:33,658
when he's been serious
with their relationship,

457
00:23:33,659 --> 00:23:35,126
giving it his all.

458
00:23:35,127 --> 00:23:37,395
I still think
he's going to choose her though.

459
00:23:37,396 --> 00:23:38,396
For the final decision?

460
00:23:38,397 --> 00:23:40,999
He's already too into her.

461
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:41,834
He likes her.

462
00:23:42,034 --> 00:23:43,168
Thank you.

463
00:23:43,169 --> 00:23:44,970
No, I'm the one
who should be thanking you.

464
00:23:44,971 --> 00:23:46,471
(The final meeting
Kim Hyun Jun and Kim Hyun Jin's mothers)

465
00:23:46,472 --> 00:23:49,574
I never thought
you'd ask to have a talk with me.

466
00:23:49,575 --> 00:23:52,144
Hyun Jun and I talked
all night last night.

467
00:23:52,145 --> 00:23:53,745
Honestly speaking,

468
00:23:53,746 --> 00:23:57,415
in the beginning, I told Hyun Jun...

469
00:23:57,416 --> 00:23:59,284
that he should go talk to Hyun Jin.

470
00:23:59,285 --> 00:24:01,454
That's what I told him,

471
00:24:01,888 --> 00:24:06,325
but I think Hyun Jun was hurt a bit.

472
00:24:06,993 --> 00:24:07,993
I think so too.

473
00:24:07,994 --> 00:24:09,928
I could tell that he was down,

474
00:24:09,929 --> 00:24:13,398
but that was when Hyun Jin came
and told him that she liked him.

475
00:24:13,399 --> 00:24:15,800
So, Hyun Jun told me...

476
00:24:15,801 --> 00:24:18,837
that he thought
she was such an amazing person.

477
00:24:18,838 --> 00:24:22,174
He said that he felt flutters
more than he thought he would.

478
00:24:22,175 --> 00:24:23,975
Hyun Jin told me this
after the date yesterday.

479
00:24:23,976 --> 00:24:26,678
She said she had seen another side of him.

480
00:24:26,679 --> 00:24:27,814
I asked her what it was,

481
00:24:29,115 --> 00:24:31,149
and she said she was really touched...

482
00:24:31,150 --> 00:24:34,152
by how he took care of you
when you were sick.

483
00:24:34,153 --> 00:24:38,790
If he's that kind of person,
wouldn't he treat his wife well too?

484
00:24:38,791 --> 00:24:39,991
Of course.

485
00:24:39,992 --> 00:24:42,962
Hyun Jun will be so good to you.

486
00:24:44,363 --> 00:24:49,068
No doubt at all. I can tell already.

487
00:24:49,902 --> 00:24:53,840
He'll be just like your son.

488
00:24:54,974 --> 00:24:57,476
I think Hyun Jun...

489
00:24:57,477 --> 00:25:01,079
will choose Hyun Jin as his final choice.

490
00:25:01,080 --> 00:25:06,052
I actually told him in the beginning
that I liked Hyun Jin,

491
00:25:06,752 --> 00:25:09,255
so I'm very satisfied right now.

492
00:25:11,657 --> 00:25:18,064
(Who is Kim Myo Jin's mother
having her final meeting with?)

493
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:22,200
Hello.

494
00:25:22,201 --> 00:25:23,969
- Thank you for coming.
- Of course.

495
00:25:23,970 --> 00:25:25,837
- Please sit.
- Thank you.

496
00:25:25,838 --> 00:25:28,007
(Kim Myo Jin and Moon Se Hoon's mothers)

497
00:25:28,941 --> 00:25:30,776
- Why do I feel anxious?
- Right?

498
00:25:31,377 --> 00:25:32,477
This feels real.

499
00:25:32,478 --> 00:25:34,613
I don't know what I should be asking...

500
00:25:34,614 --> 00:25:36,715
(An awkward meeting between the mothers.)

501
00:25:36,716 --> 00:25:40,786
Please don't hesitate to ask me anything.

502
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:44,624
Has Se Hoon made up his mind?

503
00:25:45,324 --> 00:25:49,694
I think he still has concerns.

504
00:25:49,695 --> 00:25:51,163
What about Myo Jin?

505
00:25:51,164 --> 00:25:53,698
Same with her, I think.

506
00:25:53,699 --> 00:25:54,733
Right?

507
00:25:54,734 --> 00:25:59,672
I'm curious
as to what you think about Myo Jin.

508
00:26:00,306 --> 00:26:03,441
Yes, of course. I've been thinking of her.

509
00:26:03,442 --> 00:26:05,177
She's really sweet,

510
00:26:05,178 --> 00:26:10,081
and when I saw her up close yesterday,
she was such a pretty girl.

511
00:26:10,082 --> 00:26:11,350
Today, actually...

512
00:26:13,519 --> 00:26:17,690
You've also been thinking of
another person as well, right?

513
00:26:18,524 --> 00:26:20,692
Yes, I've been looking at other people.

514
00:26:20,693 --> 00:26:22,061
Yes, so...

515
00:26:22,562 --> 00:26:24,729
This morning...

516
00:26:24,730 --> 00:26:25,731
Coffee...

517
00:26:28,134 --> 00:26:32,437
She actually walked into the living room
with some coffee when I was talking...

518
00:26:32,438 --> 00:26:33,940
with Hyun Jin's mother.

519
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:35,308
What's this?

520
00:26:35,309 --> 00:26:38,610
Se Hoon's mother made some coffee.

521
00:26:38,611 --> 00:26:41,614
- Se Hoon's mother?
- Really?

522
00:26:43,516 --> 00:26:45,184
So I thought, what's this?

523
00:26:46,385 --> 00:26:48,186
Se Hoon told me...

524
00:26:48,187 --> 00:26:54,459
that he was supposed to make coffee
a couple of days ago,

525
00:26:54,460 --> 00:26:55,760
so I said I'd make the coffee.

526
00:26:55,761 --> 00:26:57,930
I had actually brought
some coffee with me,

527
00:26:58,798 --> 00:27:01,000
so I said I'd make it.

528
00:27:03,102 --> 00:27:04,303
I see.

529
00:27:05,638 --> 00:27:08,274
Ask me anything you're curious about.

530
00:27:10,143 --> 00:27:14,413
I could read between the lines a little.

531
00:27:17,049 --> 00:27:18,717
When she told me that,

532
00:27:18,718 --> 00:27:23,288
I knew that she wasn't considering Myo Jin
as a potential daughter-in-law.

533
00:27:23,289 --> 00:27:27,959
She seemed to be telling me that
she thought of her as her daughter.

534
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:28,761
No, ma'am.

535
00:27:28,762 --> 00:27:32,732
My footsteps coming back felt a bit heavy.

536
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,767
(Moon Se Hoon's mother
is waiting for someone now.)

537
00:27:35,768 --> 00:27:37,736
I wonder...

538
00:27:37,737 --> 00:27:40,006
who Se Hoon's mother chose to talk to.

539
00:27:40,940 --> 00:27:42,340
Hello, ma'am.

540
00:27:42,341 --> 00:27:43,875
Hi, come in.

541
00:27:43,876 --> 00:27:44,710
Yes.

542
00:27:44,711 --> 00:27:46,311
- Were you surprised?
- Yes.

543
00:27:46,312 --> 00:27:49,548
- It's Myo Jin.
- I wasn't expecting it.

544
00:27:49,549 --> 00:27:50,750
I see.

545
00:27:52,151 --> 00:27:54,821
I choose Myo Jin...

546
00:27:55,087 --> 00:27:57,590
because I think
Se Hoon's interested in her.

547
00:27:58,658 --> 00:28:02,260
It'll be brief,
but I wanted to talk to her...

548
00:28:02,261 --> 00:28:04,363
and have this time with her.

549
00:28:07,166 --> 00:28:09,501
I think Se Hoon
is really interested in you.

550
00:28:09,502 --> 00:28:11,303
- Really?
- Yeah.

551
00:28:11,304 --> 00:28:12,638
How do you feel?

552
00:28:13,573 --> 00:28:16,908
I'm also interested.

553
00:28:16,909 --> 00:28:21,012
I think that's why
I kept approaching him and stuff.

554
00:28:21,013 --> 00:28:22,447
Did you?

555
00:28:22,448 --> 00:28:23,715
Yes, ma'am.

556
00:28:23,716 --> 00:28:25,617
The thing is...

557
00:28:25,618 --> 00:28:28,588
I don't know how I should say it,

558
00:28:28,855 --> 00:28:32,190
but he doesn't have a lot right now.

559
00:28:32,191 --> 00:28:33,125
Right.

560
00:28:34,193 --> 00:28:37,462
Plus, his work itself...

561
00:28:37,463 --> 00:28:41,400
doesn't give him a regular schedule.

562
00:28:42,335 --> 00:28:45,170
There are lots of work trips too.

563
00:28:45,171 --> 00:28:47,739
- Overseas.
- Right.

564
00:28:47,740 --> 00:28:51,577
It will be difficult to make time...

565
00:28:52,578 --> 00:28:54,546
for each other.

566
00:28:54,547 --> 00:28:56,381
Do you think you two...

567
00:28:56,382 --> 00:28:59,918
could work that out
and understand each other?

568
00:28:59,919 --> 00:29:01,219
You're concerned.

569
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:02,220
Yes.

570
00:29:02,221 --> 00:29:04,357
I think Se Hoon
wants to give it a try, but...

571
00:29:05,091 --> 00:29:10,462
I've never actually dated
someone who's always on the go,

572
00:29:10,463 --> 00:29:12,597
someone in his field of work, before.

573
00:29:12,598 --> 00:29:14,566
It's hard to predict how busy he'll be.

574
00:29:14,567 --> 00:29:16,568
We've never texted each other,

575
00:29:16,569 --> 00:29:19,838
and it's not like we've tried
to contact each other outside of this.

576
00:29:19,839 --> 00:29:23,074
Right, both people
need to trust each other for that.

577
00:29:23,075 --> 00:29:27,713
I'm concerned
if you could understand those things.

578
00:29:31,250 --> 00:29:33,685
You also need to know...

579
00:29:33,686 --> 00:29:37,256
that businesses can flop anytime.

580
00:29:38,157 --> 00:29:41,426
I also have a daughter,

581
00:29:41,427 --> 00:29:43,729
and if I were to choose
her partner for her,

582
00:29:44,597 --> 00:29:45,998
I...

583
00:29:46,566 --> 00:29:50,436
wouldn't choose someone
who has their own business.

584
00:29:51,637 --> 00:29:53,306
Did she call her to persuade her?

585
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,441
To make her give up?

586
00:29:57,810 --> 00:30:01,947
I don't think a guy running a business
is a good type.

587
00:30:01,948 --> 00:30:04,850
But if he has a wife by his side,

588
00:30:04,851 --> 00:30:07,887
it would be nice
for her to help him with it, right?

589
00:30:08,521 --> 00:30:10,856
I do think it would be nice
if there was someone like that,

590
00:30:10,857 --> 00:30:13,526
but I'm not sure what he thinks.

591
00:30:14,293 --> 00:30:15,328
The thing is...

592
00:30:18,297 --> 00:30:20,433
Anyway, life is...

593
00:30:20,933 --> 00:30:22,668
It can't be all sunshine and roses.

594
00:30:23,236 --> 00:30:25,137
It can't be all sunshine and roses.

595
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:30,142
Wait, this is...

596
00:30:30,143 --> 00:30:33,279
I think she's trying to scare her.

597
00:30:34,447 --> 00:30:37,182
Does she really like me?

598
00:30:37,183 --> 00:30:38,817
That's what I thought.

599
00:30:38,818 --> 00:30:42,287
Plus, running a business
isn't a stable job,

600
00:30:42,288 --> 00:30:46,358
so it seemed like she was asking
if I would be able to handle it.

601
00:30:46,359 --> 00:30:49,594
That's when I was reminded of the reality,

602
00:30:49,595 --> 00:30:50,729
and I was...

603
00:30:50,730 --> 00:30:53,599
It felt a bit suffocating then.

604
00:30:55,801 --> 00:30:56,868
Hello, ma'am.

605
00:30:56,869 --> 00:30:57,703
(Another mother has called for Myo Jin.)

606
00:30:57,704 --> 00:30:59,605
Myo Jin is popular today.

607
00:31:00,439 --> 00:31:03,575
- How pretty you are.
- Really?

608
00:31:03,576 --> 00:31:04,644
Thank you.

609
00:31:04,977 --> 00:31:08,914
You look so beautiful today.

610
00:31:08,915 --> 00:31:10,716
Because I was seeing you.

611
00:31:11,784 --> 00:31:13,019
Thank you.

612
00:31:15,321 --> 00:31:17,389
I hope Seung Hak
finds a good person here.

613
00:31:17,390 --> 00:31:18,224
Right.

614
00:31:18,225 --> 00:31:20,593
I noticed that he's...

615
00:31:21,561 --> 00:31:23,762
always the same, in a good way.

616
00:31:23,763 --> 00:31:24,664
Right?

617
00:31:24,665 --> 00:31:28,434
If he marries you,

618
00:31:28,935 --> 00:31:31,570
he'll really listen to you,
like a good husband.

619
00:31:31,571 --> 00:31:32,905
Isn't that the best husband?

620
00:31:33,206 --> 00:31:34,606
Of course.

621
00:31:34,607 --> 00:31:36,575
- Then, there won't be fights.
- Right.

622
00:31:36,576 --> 00:31:38,543
He'll be so good to his wife.

623
00:31:38,544 --> 00:31:39,512
Right.

624
00:31:40,213 --> 00:31:41,847
He'll totally treat her like a queen.

625
00:31:41,848 --> 00:31:43,148
Like a queen?

626
00:31:43,149 --> 00:31:45,650
(Nonstop flirting with her son)

627
00:31:45,651 --> 00:31:47,053
That's great.

628
00:31:48,454 --> 00:31:53,258
Do you think I fit the daughter-in-law...

629
00:31:53,259 --> 00:31:56,361
that you've always wanted?

630
00:31:56,362 --> 00:31:57,897
Yes.

631
00:31:58,931 --> 00:32:00,366
It's you, Myo Jin.

632
00:32:02,635 --> 00:32:03,402
(Her love for Myo Jin can't be stopped.)

633
00:32:03,403 --> 00:32:04,469
She didn't hesitate.

634
00:32:04,470 --> 00:32:05,471
Love for Myo Jin.

635
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:10,208
Even if I can't always be there 100%
for him?

636
00:32:10,209 --> 00:32:10,877
Yes.

637
00:32:10,877 --> 00:32:11,844
Of course.

638
00:32:13,546 --> 00:32:15,248
You're so amazing.

639
00:32:17,083 --> 00:32:20,987
His mother is so amazing.

640
00:32:21,354 --> 00:32:24,489
I could actually see myself
living a peaceful family life.

641
00:32:24,490 --> 00:32:28,093
I thought we'd make
a very comfortable family...

642
00:32:28,094 --> 00:32:32,164
with a husband
I wouldn't have to wait for.

643
00:32:32,165 --> 00:32:34,167
It made me imagine a life like that.

644
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:36,768
Right. The vibe is very different.

645
00:32:36,769 --> 00:32:39,671
However, I don't think it'll affect...

646
00:32:39,672 --> 00:32:41,139
- No?
- her.

647
00:32:41,140 --> 00:32:43,308
You marry the person you like.

648
00:32:43,309 --> 00:32:44,709
You're not living with his mother.

649
00:32:44,710 --> 00:32:45,710
You need to like him.

650
00:32:45,711 --> 00:32:47,914
That's true, but when you get married...

651
00:32:48,481 --> 00:32:51,049
You can't really do that...

652
00:32:51,050 --> 00:32:53,085
It's hard with your husband's mother.

653
00:32:56,422 --> 00:33:01,126
First, I met Seung Hak's mother.

654
00:33:01,127 --> 00:33:02,327
She was so amazing.

655
00:33:02,328 --> 00:33:03,962
Yeah, I told you she was.

656
00:33:03,963 --> 00:33:05,897
She was great.

657
00:33:05,898 --> 00:33:07,132
Very nice,

658
00:33:07,133 --> 00:33:10,068
but it's funny because...

659
00:33:10,069 --> 00:33:13,472
with Se Hoon, it was kind of the opposite.

660
00:33:13,473 --> 00:33:18,477
It made me concerned after talking to her.

661
00:33:18,478 --> 00:33:19,312
Why?

662
00:33:19,313 --> 00:33:24,484
I think it could be hard for me...

663
00:33:25,518 --> 00:33:28,086
with his business and all.

664
00:33:28,087 --> 00:33:30,655
If we do get married,

665
00:33:30,656 --> 00:33:33,925
I thought that it could be hard,

666
00:33:33,926 --> 00:33:36,728
but if I get married to Seung Hak,

667
00:33:36,729 --> 00:33:39,598
it'd be comfortable.

668
00:33:39,599 --> 00:33:41,666
Right, comfortable.

669
00:33:41,667 --> 00:33:45,705
I think it would be a happy marriage.

670
00:33:46,305 --> 00:33:49,909
The thing is, Se Hoon's mother...

671
00:33:51,444 --> 00:33:53,278
might not agree to the decision.

672
00:33:53,279 --> 00:33:54,914
Right? That's that too.

673
00:33:57,917 --> 00:33:59,719
Did you have a good talk?
What did you talk about?

674
00:34:01,921 --> 00:34:02,788
Just...

675
00:34:05,024 --> 00:34:05,925
Just...

676
00:34:05,926 --> 00:34:07,058
Was it just casual?

677
00:34:07,059 --> 00:34:07,927
Yeah.

678
00:34:08,794 --> 00:34:10,196
Have you made up your mind?

679
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:20,406
(Even more conflicted
after the final meeting.)

680
00:34:21,774 --> 00:34:23,041
It's all mixed up.

681
00:34:23,042 --> 00:34:24,743
(What will their final decisions be?)

682
00:34:24,744 --> 00:34:27,747
For now, Min Cheol and Jin Joo...

683
00:34:28,014 --> 00:34:30,649
seem to be sure of each other.

684
00:34:30,650 --> 00:34:32,951
Earlier, when she told him
to take her purse,

685
00:34:32,952 --> 00:34:34,619
- he took it without hesitating.
- Very naturally.

686
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:36,588
She didn't even tell him.
It was very natural.

687
00:34:36,589 --> 00:34:41,293
Things are pretty unclear
with Cho Eun Na Rae and Han Gyeol.

688
00:34:41,294 --> 00:34:45,197
They're the most
unpredictable couple right now.

689
00:34:45,198 --> 00:34:50,303
For me, besides Eun Na Rae's mother,

690
00:34:50,736 --> 00:34:53,506
I think the rest of the three...

691
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:56,142
will choose someone, no matter what.

692
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,511
This is hard.

693
00:34:59,846 --> 00:35:00,580
(It's time for the final decision.)

694
00:35:00,581 --> 00:35:02,013
- Finally.
- It's time.

695
00:35:02,014 --> 00:35:03,149
It's the love tower.

696
00:35:04,317 --> 00:35:05,784
It's time to make the final decision.

697
00:35:05,785 --> 00:35:08,788
(The sons and daughters will make
their decisions first.)

698
00:35:12,825 --> 00:35:15,227
(Women have white roses.)

699
00:35:15,228 --> 00:35:17,763
(Men have red roses.)

700
00:35:18,097 --> 00:35:19,831
(They will give their rose
to their final choice.)

701
00:35:19,832 --> 00:35:21,601
Alright.

702
00:35:22,101 --> 00:35:24,603
The sons and daughters
will make their final decisions first,

703
00:35:24,604 --> 00:35:28,106
then the mothers
can either agree or disagree...

704
00:35:28,107 --> 00:35:30,342
for the final couple.

705
00:35:30,343 --> 00:35:34,881
Therefore, only the couples
who get their mothers' approvals...

706
00:35:35,181 --> 00:35:39,017
- will become the final couple.
- That's how they'll be finalized.

707
00:35:39,018 --> 00:35:40,619
That's how they become final.

708
00:35:40,620 --> 00:35:41,621
This is hard.

709
00:35:42,321 --> 00:35:43,256
They must be nervous.

710
00:35:43,257 --> 00:35:48,561
(What will their choice be?)

711
00:35:51,397 --> 00:35:55,368
Alright, we'll start the final decision.

712
00:35:58,037 --> 00:36:00,339
We'll start with Kim Jin Joo.

713
00:36:01,507 --> 00:36:04,209
I've made up my mind.

714
00:36:04,210 --> 00:36:08,181
We had a few moments
where things didn't line up,

715
00:36:08,481 --> 00:36:11,918
but I think we both worked hard
to express our feelings.

716
00:36:12,952 --> 00:36:17,088
I had such a great time for six days...

717
00:36:17,089 --> 00:36:18,791
with all of you great people,

718
00:36:19,959 --> 00:36:21,961
and I hope my feelings reach you.

719
00:36:31,404 --> 00:36:34,539
(The first final decision
Kim Jin Joo chose Jang Min Cheol.)

720
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:36,442
Yes, as expected.

721
00:36:37,577 --> 00:36:40,079
Jin Joo chose...

722
00:36:40,413 --> 00:36:42,148
Min Cheol, as expected.

723
00:36:45,751 --> 00:36:47,820
Next, Kim Hyun Jin.

724
00:36:49,622 --> 00:36:53,593
It was so nice meeting
all of you like this.

725
00:36:54,126 --> 00:36:57,864
I hope we can continue this friendship.

726
00:36:58,331 --> 00:37:00,132
I won't be making the final decision.

727
00:37:00,867 --> 00:37:02,400
Yes, I thought she'd do that.

728
00:37:02,401 --> 00:37:03,803
Good choice.

729
00:37:04,403 --> 00:37:06,872
It feels bittersweet.
That's the right word.

730
00:37:06,873 --> 00:37:09,774
The timing wasn't great with Hyun Jun,

731
00:37:09,775 --> 00:37:12,077
and with Min Cheol, I wasn't...

732
00:37:12,078 --> 00:37:16,182
My feelings weren't that big for him.

733
00:37:18,518 --> 00:37:20,620
Next, Jang Min Cheol.

734
00:37:24,957 --> 00:37:29,929
I know six days probably
wasn't even enough time to go all in,

735
00:37:31,330 --> 00:37:33,299
so I'm sorry
for the times we missed each other.

736
00:37:33,866 --> 00:37:34,900
However,

737
00:37:34,901 --> 00:37:37,970
I believe that we've become stronger
after those moments,

738
00:37:39,438 --> 00:37:41,307
so I would love
to get to know each other more.

739
00:37:46,245 --> 00:37:50,183
(Jang Min Cheol chose Kim Jin Joo.)

740
00:37:50,917 --> 00:37:52,017
Let's go.

741
00:37:52,018 --> 00:37:53,151
Where?

742
00:37:53,152 --> 00:37:54,219
To get approved.

743
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,620
Right, they need approval.

744
00:37:55,621 --> 00:37:57,857
Yes, I need to go
get their decisions approved.

745
00:38:01,060 --> 00:38:03,196
I like someone like Jin Joo who's honest.

746
00:38:03,796 --> 00:38:06,132
Plus, she's cute.

747
00:38:08,234 --> 00:38:09,435
I feel like...

748
00:38:09,969 --> 00:38:13,172
someone like me
needs to stay with Jin Joo.

749
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:16,174
- They look good.
- Yes.

750
00:38:16,175 --> 00:38:17,676
Congratulations.

751
00:38:17,677 --> 00:38:19,911
They've become a couple for now.

752
00:38:19,912 --> 00:38:21,848
Jang Min Cheol and Kim Jin Joo.

753
00:38:23,216 --> 00:38:24,316
(Kim Hyun Jun's final decision)

754
00:38:24,317 --> 00:38:25,151
Yes.

755
00:38:25,685 --> 00:38:29,121
Those five nights and six days
felt both short and long.

756
00:38:30,122 --> 00:38:32,290
It was happy but also hard,

757
00:38:32,291 --> 00:38:34,693
then happy and hard again.

758
00:38:34,694 --> 00:38:37,629
Even though the days
kept repeating like that,

759
00:38:37,630 --> 00:38:39,265
I think it was a good experience.

760
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:42,969
I won't be making the final decision.

761
00:38:48,608 --> 00:38:52,678
(Kim Hyun Jun
gave up on his final decision.)

762
00:38:52,979 --> 00:38:55,348
Maybe I should've opened up earlier.

763
00:38:55,748 --> 00:38:59,085
Then, with that open mind,
I should've looked into all the choices...

764
00:38:59,952 --> 00:39:02,320
with a slow approach.

765
00:39:02,321 --> 00:39:04,190
I feel sad that I couldn't do that.

766
00:39:10,796 --> 00:39:13,099
It's Se Hoon's turn now.

767
00:39:14,367 --> 00:39:16,902
I wasn't sure as to who...

768
00:39:16,903 --> 00:39:19,738
I should choose
out of the two people in my mind.

769
00:39:19,739 --> 00:39:22,542
I looked back on my feelings,

770
00:39:23,176 --> 00:39:26,145
and asked myself who I should choose.

771
00:39:31,818 --> 00:39:32,952
I hope...

772
00:39:33,719 --> 00:39:36,622
that I get to see the first snow together
with you this winter.

773
00:39:43,129 --> 00:39:45,130
I think you'd be so nervous
to see the person come to you.

774
00:39:45,131 --> 00:39:46,799
I know, right?

775
00:39:52,972 --> 00:39:55,073
He chose Myo Jin.

776
00:39:55,074 --> 00:39:58,444
(Moon Se Hoon chose Kim Myo Jin.)

777
00:40:04,317 --> 00:40:09,055
There were moments in the morning
that made me more and more certain.

778
00:40:09,655 --> 00:40:13,024
I could finally see the love and warmth...

779
00:40:13,025 --> 00:40:14,760
from the way...

780
00:40:15,428 --> 00:40:19,164
Myo Jin looked at me. I could feel it.

781
00:40:19,165 --> 00:40:23,002
That was what really opened my heart,

782
00:40:23,469 --> 00:40:28,140
and that was when
she wasn't the better choice...

783
00:40:28,141 --> 00:40:29,374
but the only choice for me.

784
00:40:29,375 --> 00:40:32,145
It was a decisive moment,
a moment of conviction.

785
00:40:37,283 --> 00:40:41,052
(Lee Seung Hak's final decision)

786
00:40:41,053 --> 00:40:42,855
Thank you for giving me...

787
00:40:43,890 --> 00:40:46,692
an experience
I'd probably never have otherwise.

788
00:40:49,495 --> 00:40:52,497
I felt butterflies from start to finish.

789
00:40:52,498 --> 00:40:53,466
Nice.

790
00:40:53,733 --> 00:40:54,967
What a nice finisher.

791
00:40:59,872 --> 00:41:02,274
(Lee Seung Hak chose Kim Myo Jin.)

792
00:41:02,275 --> 00:41:03,708
He chose her.

793
00:41:03,709 --> 00:41:06,511
- That's cool.
- Yeah, I mean,

794
00:41:06,512 --> 00:41:09,782
he showed everything on this,
so how could he pass on the decision?

795
00:41:10,316 --> 00:41:12,284
Seung Hak is so cool.
He's been constant from start to finish.

796
00:41:12,285 --> 00:41:13,653
Yes, totally.

797
00:41:17,924 --> 00:41:24,897
(Kim Myo Jin has been chosen
by Moon Se Hoon and Lee Seung Hak.)

798
00:41:26,666 --> 00:41:28,533
Myo Jin had two votes now.

799
00:41:28,534 --> 00:41:30,336
I wonder who she'll choose.

800
00:41:32,305 --> 00:41:36,942
All these complicated thoughts
kept coming into my mind.

801
00:41:36,943 --> 00:41:39,778
If I consider their family...

802
00:41:39,779 --> 00:41:41,847
and his life patterns,

803
00:41:41,848 --> 00:41:44,316
Seung Hak seems like
the perfect match for me,

804
00:41:44,317 --> 00:41:48,286
but the person I'm drawn to...

805
00:41:48,287 --> 00:41:49,921
is Se Hoon.

806
00:41:49,922 --> 00:41:54,193
The thought of getting married
is what's making it so complicated,

807
00:41:55,795 --> 00:41:57,195
but I should follow my heart.

808
00:41:57,196 --> 00:41:58,064
Right.

809
00:42:00,666 --> 00:42:05,338
Thank you all for being with me
through this time, short yet long.

810
00:42:08,941 --> 00:42:13,379
I will go to the person
who has made my heart flutter.

811
00:42:18,251 --> 00:42:23,122
(Who will Kim Myo Jin choose?)

812
00:42:28,561 --> 00:42:33,198
(Kim Myo Jin chose Moon Se Hoon.)

813
00:42:33,199 --> 00:42:35,033
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

814
00:42:35,034 --> 00:42:36,468
How great is this?

815
00:42:36,469 --> 00:42:37,636
I'm sorry.

816
00:42:37,637 --> 00:42:38,770
- I'd like to stop you.
- What?

817
00:42:38,771 --> 00:42:41,973
- We still have the mothers' choices left.
- That's true, but...

818
00:42:41,974 --> 00:42:43,609
They chose each other.

819
00:42:46,445 --> 00:42:50,850
(The first final decision
Kim Myo Jin and Moon Se Hoon)

820
00:42:56,923 --> 00:43:00,158
In the end, my heart needs to be there.

821
00:43:00,159 --> 00:43:02,060
The person who was on my mind more.

822
00:43:02,061 --> 00:43:03,963
That was Se Hoon.

823
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:09,201
Now, it's Eun Na Rae.

824
00:43:09,202 --> 00:43:11,303
We can't forget about them.

825
00:43:11,304 --> 00:43:13,438
There was interest,

826
00:43:13,439 --> 00:43:17,576
but it felt a bit overwhelming
to approach him just casually.

827
00:43:17,577 --> 00:43:19,946
I don't know
if I should make the decision or not.

828
00:43:29,755 --> 00:43:35,661
I've met a lot of great
and beautiful people here,

829
00:43:38,631 --> 00:43:44,937
but I'd like to give this rose to someone
who shone especially brightly for me.

830
00:43:51,177 --> 00:43:57,083
(Cho Eun Na Rae chose Seo Han Gyeol.)

831
00:43:57,550 --> 00:44:00,318
He's the one who caught my eyes...

832
00:44:00,319 --> 00:44:05,157
as soon as I stepped in here,

833
00:44:05,158 --> 00:44:08,126
and I think he turned out...

834
00:44:08,127 --> 00:44:11,063
to be a way better person than I thought.

835
00:44:11,430 --> 00:44:15,201
So, I'd love to get to know him more.

836
00:44:17,570 --> 00:44:21,006
(Seo Han Gyeol
will make his final decision.)

837
00:44:21,007 --> 00:44:22,041
Han Gyeol looks a bit...

838
00:44:23,342 --> 00:44:25,678
I was so conflicted.

839
00:44:27,880 --> 00:44:31,950
I kept asking myself
if this was going to be okay.

840
00:44:31,951 --> 00:44:36,155
Either way,
I find myself thinking about it a lot.

841
00:44:37,123 --> 00:44:38,757
Why do you think he cried in the morning?

842
00:44:38,758 --> 00:44:40,525
I'm curious too,
and I wonder what he wrote in the letter.

843
00:44:40,526 --> 00:44:42,260
Me too. I want to know as well.

844
00:44:42,261 --> 00:44:43,929
Do you think he'll make the decision?

845
00:44:43,930 --> 00:44:44,930
I don't think so.

846
00:44:44,931 --> 00:44:46,464
- You don't think so?
- I don't think so.

847
00:44:46,465 --> 00:44:47,666
- What about you?
- I think he'll make the decision.

848
00:44:47,667 --> 00:44:49,435
You think so? I think so too.

849
00:44:50,102 --> 00:44:51,436
I think he'll still make the choice.

850
00:44:51,437 --> 00:44:54,207
(Will Seo Han Gyeol
make the final decision?)

851
00:44:56,008 --> 00:44:59,846
(Han Gyeol can't seem to start talking.)

852
00:45:08,054 --> 00:45:13,692
Thank you to all the participants
for this heartwarming experience,

853
00:45:13,693 --> 00:45:15,861
and thank you to all the staff.

854
00:45:15,862 --> 00:45:18,431
I don't think
I've properly expressed how grateful I am.

855
00:45:20,266 --> 00:45:23,569
But the person I'm most thankful for...

856
00:45:24,403 --> 00:45:27,172
is my mother who came here with me.

857
00:45:27,173 --> 00:45:30,876
People only called her
as Seo Han Gyeol's mother,

858
00:45:30,877 --> 00:45:33,713
but I'd like to express my gratitude
toward Ms. Kwon Min Seon,

859
00:45:34,647 --> 00:45:39,619
and I'm happy
to have spent the days here with you.

860
00:45:40,786 --> 00:45:41,654
No way.

861
00:45:43,456 --> 00:45:46,792
And also, Ms. Kwon Min Seon told me...

862
00:45:47,293 --> 00:45:51,497
that loving someone
is getting to know their world.

863
00:45:52,565 --> 00:45:55,334
I would like to...

864
00:45:56,802 --> 00:45:58,237
get to know...

865
00:45:59,505 --> 00:46:01,941
someone's world,

866
00:46:03,376 --> 00:46:05,144
so I will give my rose to her.

867
00:46:06,746 --> 00:46:09,481
- Really?
- He scared me there.

868
00:46:09,482 --> 00:46:11,384
I got scared for a second.

869
00:46:15,822 --> 00:46:16,822
Thank you.

870
00:46:16,823 --> 00:46:20,559
(Seo Han Gyeol chose Cho Eun Na Rae.)

871
00:46:20,560 --> 00:46:22,761
Yes, congratulations.

872
00:46:22,762 --> 00:46:24,763
Cho Eun Na Rae and Seo Han Gyeol.

873
00:46:24,764 --> 00:46:27,533
(The first final decision
Cho Eun Na Rae and Seo Han Gyeol)

874
00:46:28,301 --> 00:46:32,437
I know it looked like
I was the one conflicted,

875
00:46:32,438 --> 00:46:35,640
but I'm sure she was the one
who had lots to think about.

876
00:46:35,641 --> 00:46:37,809
I know that Eun Na Rae...

877
00:46:37,810 --> 00:46:40,446
is an amazing person,

878
00:46:41,848 --> 00:46:43,249
so I won't be giving up on her.

879
00:46:46,085 --> 00:46:49,988
(Three couples have been made.)

880
00:46:49,989 --> 00:46:52,524
Dear viewers, this isn't the end.

881
00:46:52,525 --> 00:46:53,859
There's still the mother's decision left.

882
00:46:53,860 --> 00:46:54,993
We still have to get their approvals.

883
00:46:54,994 --> 00:46:58,864
Both mothers have to approve...

884
00:46:58,865 --> 00:47:02,501
in order for them to be a final couple.

885
00:47:02,502 --> 00:47:04,236
Do you think anyone would disapprove?

886
00:47:04,237 --> 00:47:07,172
I think Han Gyeol's mother
is going to disapprove.

887
00:47:07,173 --> 00:47:09,875
She will say no,

888
00:47:09,876 --> 00:47:11,710
and for the rest...

889
00:47:11,711 --> 00:47:14,013
- I think they will all approve.
- Yes.

890
00:47:14,647 --> 00:47:17,583
(The last step
to becoming the final couple)

891
00:47:17,884 --> 00:47:21,988
(The mother's decision)

892
00:47:22,421 --> 00:47:25,558
(The couple waits
for their mothers' decisions.)

893
00:47:26,259 --> 00:47:28,094
If they approve, they walk in?

894
00:47:29,061 --> 00:47:30,496
If they don't, they'll leave?

895
00:47:31,397 --> 00:47:35,434
(Will the mothers
open the door and walk in?)

896
00:47:36,035 --> 00:47:41,474
(Kim Jin Joo and Jang Min Cheol
waits for their mothers' decisions.)

897
00:47:42,375 --> 00:47:44,943
Now we wait for the mother's decision.

898
00:47:44,944 --> 00:47:49,081
(How will the mothers decide?)

899
00:47:57,323 --> 00:47:58,390
(Kim Jin Joo's mother approves)

900
00:47:58,391 --> 00:48:00,125
As expected from her mother.

901
00:48:00,126 --> 00:48:02,028
Jin Joo's mother.

902
00:48:08,000 --> 00:48:08,935
Mother, welcome.

903
00:48:13,706 --> 00:48:14,807
Yes, I approve.

904
00:48:15,942 --> 00:48:19,579
The person whom Jin Joo likes
is the person I like.

905
00:48:19,979 --> 00:48:22,181
I believe that Min Cheol
is the right person.

906
00:48:23,349 --> 00:48:24,983
I'm tearing up.

907
00:48:24,984 --> 00:48:26,953
Seeing Jin Joo smile made me so happy.

908
00:48:28,488 --> 00:48:31,056
Mother, it's been hard, we know.

909
00:48:31,057 --> 00:48:32,959
- Right.
- You are amazing.

910
00:48:34,460 --> 00:48:37,329
(Now, we wait for one more person.)

911
00:48:37,330 --> 00:48:43,870
(What will Min Cheol's mother's
decision be?)

912
00:48:45,671 --> 00:48:46,938
Of course.

913
00:48:46,939 --> 00:48:48,440
Congratulations.

914
00:48:48,441 --> 00:48:50,309
(Jang Min Cheol's mother approves.)

915
00:48:52,345 --> 00:48:57,049
(Both mothers approve
of their relationship.)

916
00:48:59,318 --> 00:49:00,785
Yes, I approve.

917
00:49:00,786 --> 00:49:02,688
I approve 100%.

918
00:49:03,856 --> 00:49:06,324
She's someone my son chose,

919
00:49:06,325 --> 00:49:09,862
so right from the start, I liked her.

920
00:49:13,065 --> 00:49:15,066
I'm standing beside your son here.

921
00:49:15,067 --> 00:49:16,102
Good choice.

922
00:49:18,137 --> 00:49:19,371
Thank you, ma'am.

923
00:49:19,372 --> 00:49:20,672
No, thank you.

924
00:49:20,673 --> 00:49:21,873
That must feel so weird in a good way.

925
00:49:21,874 --> 00:49:22,975
Let's have a group hug like this.

926
00:49:23,643 --> 00:49:24,577
Congratulations.

927
00:49:24,578 --> 00:49:25,644
Good for you.

928
00:49:25,645 --> 00:49:28,547
It must feel so weird,
with your mother like that.

929
00:49:28,548 --> 00:49:31,717
There were moments
where we missed each other,

930
00:49:32,718 --> 00:49:36,522
but in the end, we found our way back,

931
00:49:37,323 --> 00:49:38,424
so I'm happy.

932
00:49:39,859 --> 00:49:42,060
I'm sure Jin Joo's mother...

933
00:49:42,061 --> 00:49:45,063
won't regret making this decision...

934
00:49:45,064 --> 00:49:46,532
once she trusts her with him.

935
00:49:48,401 --> 00:49:50,302
We'll become closer,

936
00:49:50,303 --> 00:49:53,371
and I plan on spending
a lot of time together...

937
00:49:53,372 --> 00:49:55,674
until we reach the goal...

938
00:49:55,675 --> 00:49:59,245
of why we decided to come on this show
in the first place.

939
00:49:59,979 --> 00:50:01,781
Jin Joo's happiness is my happiness.

940
00:50:02,648 --> 00:50:03,616
I will take that to heart.

941
00:50:05,551 --> 00:50:10,355
Alright, Jang Min Cheol and Kim Jin Joo
are officially a final couple.

942
00:50:10,356 --> 00:50:12,157
Congratulations.

943
00:50:12,158 --> 00:50:13,860
Congratulations.

944
00:50:15,428 --> 00:50:19,565
(It's time for the mothers of Kim Myo Jin
and Moon Se Hoon to decide.)

945
00:50:19,832 --> 00:50:21,267
I'm nervous.

946
00:50:25,605 --> 00:50:28,373
She needs to come in to approve?

947
00:50:28,374 --> 00:50:29,574
Is that it? Or...

948
00:50:29,575 --> 00:50:31,144
What if she comes in...

949
00:50:32,612 --> 00:50:35,481
and says no in front of us?

950
00:50:37,116 --> 00:50:39,584
Does Se Hoon's mother...

951
00:50:39,585 --> 00:50:41,253
really approve of me?

952
00:50:41,254 --> 00:50:44,924
I mean, because of all the things
I've heard otherwise...

953
00:50:45,224 --> 00:50:46,625
Maybe...

954
00:50:46,626 --> 00:50:50,796
I think there's a chance
that we might get disapproval from her.

955
00:50:51,063 --> 00:50:52,597
She must be so anxious.

956
00:50:52,598 --> 00:50:55,935
Myo Jin has heard
a lot of negative things.

957
00:51:02,175 --> 00:51:06,979
(Mothers are thinking behind the doors.)

958
00:51:08,447 --> 00:51:09,948
Why is this making me so nervous?

959
00:51:09,949 --> 00:51:10,817
I'm nervous.

960
00:51:12,585 --> 00:51:17,023
I mean, but for what reason
would they oppose it though?

961
00:51:24,797 --> 00:51:27,333
Are they really not coming?

962
00:51:27,767 --> 00:51:29,100
No, no.

963
00:51:29,101 --> 00:51:30,536
Is Se Hoon's mother opposing it?

964
00:51:31,337 --> 00:51:33,606
(No way...)

965
00:51:40,713 --> 00:51:41,980
(Moon Se Hoon's mother approves.)

966
00:51:41,981 --> 00:51:42,982
Right.

967
00:51:44,584 --> 00:51:45,885
Se Hoon's mother...

968
00:51:51,724 --> 00:51:52,792
- Thank you.
- Yes.

969
00:51:56,896 --> 00:51:58,797
Good job, Se Hoon.

970
00:51:58,798 --> 00:52:00,132
Yes, thank you.

971
00:52:00,733 --> 00:52:02,101
Come here. Come beside her.

972
00:52:04,537 --> 00:52:07,139
I believe in my son,

973
00:52:07,140 --> 00:52:11,943
so I approve of everything
my son decides on.

974
00:52:11,944 --> 00:52:14,746
We were really thinking of marriage...

975
00:52:14,747 --> 00:52:16,582
when we decided to join this program.

976
00:52:17,116 --> 00:52:20,452
I hope they have
a warm winter together, full of love,

977
00:52:20,453 --> 00:52:22,255
and I hope all the best for the two.

978
00:52:22,688 --> 00:52:27,592
She said all that to Myo Jin...

979
00:52:27,593 --> 00:52:30,562
- Because we were worried.
- Right, because she was concerned.

980
00:52:30,563 --> 00:52:32,564
- Since she has a daughter too.
- Right.

981
00:52:32,565 --> 00:52:34,399
I've already warned you.

982
00:52:34,400 --> 00:52:37,702
Don't blame me later.

983
00:52:37,703 --> 00:52:38,838
That's what she meant.

984
00:52:41,340 --> 00:52:43,009
How are you feeling?

985
00:52:43,643 --> 00:52:44,844
- Good.
- I'm glad.

986
00:52:47,647 --> 00:52:51,583
(It's time for Myo Jin's mother
to make her decision.)

987
00:52:51,584 --> 00:52:53,885
From everything we've seen so far,

988
00:52:53,886 --> 00:52:59,024
there was nothing to suggest
she'd oppose it, right?

989
00:52:59,025 --> 00:53:01,194
Right, but...

990
00:53:02,128 --> 00:53:04,496
Remember what Myo Jin's mother said?

991
00:53:04,497 --> 00:53:07,132
She said that
Se Hoon's mother might oppose it.

992
00:53:07,133 --> 00:53:09,334
Maybe Myo Jin wasn't
being considered as her daughter-in-law.

993
00:53:09,335 --> 00:53:11,102
She said that's how she felt.

994
00:53:11,103 --> 00:53:13,805
Because she made coffee that time.

995
00:53:13,806 --> 00:53:16,007
Maybe her mother might not enter.

996
00:53:16,008 --> 00:53:17,677
No, I think she will.

997
00:53:19,679 --> 00:53:26,085
(What will be
Myo Jin's mother's decision?)

998
00:53:29,889 --> 00:53:31,224
This is really...

999
00:53:31,791 --> 00:53:32,858
This tension is insane.

1000
00:53:32,859 --> 00:53:34,594
Yes, it's really...

1001
00:53:39,765 --> 00:53:41,533
(Myo Jin's mother
is deep in thought behind the door.)

1002
00:53:41,534 --> 00:53:42,668
She must be thinking.

1003
00:53:56,115 --> 00:53:59,152
Kim Myo Jin's mother
has not approved the decision.

1004
00:54:00,052 --> 00:54:02,205
(Pardon?)

1005
00:54:02,245 --> 00:54:03,979
(We haven't paused the screen.)

1006
00:54:03,980 --> 00:54:04,781
No way.

1007
00:54:04,782 --> 00:54:06,248
- See? I told you.
- Why?

1008
00:54:06,249 --> 00:54:07,484
I told you.

1009
00:54:08,218 --> 00:54:09,952
I told you so.

1010
00:54:09,953 --> 00:54:10,821
But...

1011
00:54:11,355 --> 00:54:13,789
There's been no sign she'd be against it.

1012
00:54:13,790 --> 00:54:16,993
But she did say earlier
about the nuance she got.

1013
00:54:17,427 --> 00:54:20,296
She thought that Se Hoon's mother...

1014
00:54:20,297 --> 00:54:23,966
wasn't considering Myo Jin
as a potential daughter-in-law.

1015
00:54:23,967 --> 00:54:25,501
But still...

1016
00:54:25,502 --> 00:54:27,303
I don't know. Why did she do that?

1017
00:54:27,304 --> 00:54:29,905
The mothers don't know
about each other's decisions.

1018
00:54:29,906 --> 00:54:31,640
Then, in any case,

1019
00:54:31,641 --> 00:54:35,077
you need to go in for anything
to have a chance of happening.

1020
00:54:35,078 --> 00:54:35,846
Right.

1021
00:54:35,847 --> 00:54:38,314
If I give up first...

1022
00:54:38,315 --> 00:54:39,482
Maybe she was offended?

1023
00:54:39,483 --> 00:54:41,952
I'm really curious as to why?

1024
00:54:42,586 --> 00:54:45,588
Kim Myo Jin's mother
has not approved the decision.

1025
00:54:45,589 --> 00:54:52,529
(Kim Myo Jin's mother disapproves.)

1026
00:54:58,001 --> 00:54:59,535
That's a sudden plot twist.

1027
00:54:59,536 --> 00:55:00,404
Why?

1028
00:55:00,704 --> 00:55:03,939
Myo Jin must be feeling
so awkward between them.

1029
00:55:03,940 --> 00:55:05,308
Of course.

1030
00:55:09,146 --> 00:55:13,250
(Myo Jin's mother leaves
without entering through the door.)

1031
00:55:13,750 --> 00:55:17,787
I got concerned.

1032
00:55:17,788 --> 00:55:21,957
I had a conversation
with Se Hoon's mother this morning.

1033
00:55:21,958 --> 00:55:25,161
I got the feeling that she was...

1034
00:55:25,162 --> 00:55:28,164
considering another person for Se Hoon.

1035
00:55:28,165 --> 00:55:30,633
Even if they do become a couple,

1036
00:55:30,634 --> 00:55:36,339
the things that were to follow
really worried me.

1037
00:55:36,340 --> 00:55:37,274
See?

1038
00:55:37,274 --> 00:55:38,141
I told you so.

1039
00:55:38,142 --> 00:55:40,009
See? I told you.

1040
00:55:40,010 --> 00:55:43,212
Of course, you want the mother-in-law...

1041
00:55:43,213 --> 00:55:46,982
to dote on your daughter
and be kind to her.

1042
00:55:46,983 --> 00:55:50,787
It was a misunderstanding,
but in that situation...

1043
00:55:51,188 --> 00:55:53,523
I totally get
where her concerns are coming from.

1044
00:55:55,025 --> 00:55:58,427
Of course, in that moment,

1045
00:55:58,428 --> 00:56:02,098
it didn't feel good, but...

1046
00:56:02,099 --> 00:56:03,332
It's a misunderstanding.

1047
00:56:03,333 --> 00:56:06,670
I think I should accept it as it is.

1048
00:56:07,270 --> 00:56:10,373
I'm thankful to Myo Jin for choosing me,

1049
00:56:10,374 --> 00:56:14,878
so I want to focus on something good
rather than bad,

1050
00:56:16,780 --> 00:56:18,415
and wrap this up on a good note.

1051
00:56:20,217 --> 00:56:22,385
I think my mother
might be feeling disappointed,

1052
00:56:22,386 --> 00:56:23,920
so I'm worried about that.

1053
00:56:24,855 --> 00:56:29,525
She must feel like
her son was disapproved...

1054
00:56:29,526 --> 00:56:34,331
and rejected,
so she probably feels quite upset.

1055
00:56:35,332 --> 00:56:40,137
It's disappointing. It is.

1056
00:56:40,437 --> 00:56:44,340
I guess she felt like he wasn't enough,

1057
00:56:44,341 --> 00:56:46,709
and that thought...

1058
00:56:46,710 --> 00:56:50,913
makes me feel a bit bitter,
if I'm being honest.

1059
00:56:50,914 --> 00:56:53,283
I'm Se Hoon's mother, so...

1060
00:56:54,685 --> 00:56:56,520
It's a bit...

1061
00:56:59,723 --> 00:57:02,324
Honestly, it's a bit confusing.

1062
00:57:02,325 --> 00:57:05,928
I think if we became a couple,

1063
00:57:05,929 --> 00:57:07,863
she thought...

1064
00:57:07,864 --> 00:57:09,965
we might have to get married right away.

1065
00:57:09,966 --> 00:57:15,571
That's probably one of the things
she was worried about.

1066
00:57:15,572 --> 00:57:19,241
Plus, she must've thought
that Se Hoon's mother might oppose it.

1067
00:57:19,242 --> 00:57:22,678
In that case, she probably wanted
to protect her daughter.

1068
00:57:22,679 --> 00:57:26,282
I think those were her thoughts.

1069
00:57:26,283 --> 00:57:28,451
The choice is a bit disappointing,

1070
00:57:28,452 --> 00:57:31,455
but this isn't the end,
so I don't want to dwell on it.

1071
00:57:32,522 --> 00:57:34,690
How disappointing.

1072
00:57:34,691 --> 00:57:36,292
The two of them...

1073
00:57:36,293 --> 00:57:39,228
really hit it off at the end...

1074
00:57:39,229 --> 00:57:41,198
and were sure of their feelings.

1075
00:57:41,598 --> 00:57:43,733
- On the last day.
- Yes.

1076
00:57:43,734 --> 00:57:45,702
It could've been different
if they had one more day.

1077
00:57:47,104 --> 00:57:49,538
Now, it's time for the last couple,
Seo Han Gyeol and Cho Eun Na Rae.

1078
00:57:49,539 --> 00:57:51,640
Do you think your mother would disapprove?

1079
00:57:51,641 --> 00:57:53,010
She might not approve.

1080
00:57:55,012 --> 00:57:56,046
Really?

1081
00:57:59,349 --> 00:58:00,283
It's not over until it's over.

1082
00:58:01,852 --> 00:58:05,855
(A nerve-racking moment
as they wait for their mothers' decisions)

1083
00:58:05,856 --> 00:58:10,192
This is the highlight of this section.

1084
00:58:10,193 --> 00:58:11,260
Yes, it is.

1085
00:58:11,261 --> 00:58:13,162
The last couple
caught me off guard, though.

1086
00:58:13,163 --> 00:58:14,965
Yeah, I was so surprised.

1087
00:58:19,636 --> 00:58:23,606
I knew she was really concerned.

1088
00:58:23,607 --> 00:58:25,574
Even if my mom disapproves,
can I disapprove that?

1089
00:58:25,575 --> 00:58:27,243
Those thoughts
were going through my mind,

1090
00:58:27,244 --> 00:58:28,845
but I told her...

1091
00:58:29,513 --> 00:58:32,115
to do what you think is fit.

1092
00:58:32,582 --> 00:58:36,620
For this couple, they both sort of know
the outcome already.

1093
00:58:48,265 --> 00:58:49,398
(Cho Eun Na Rae's mother approves.)

1094
00:58:49,399 --> 00:58:51,435
Yes, Eun Na Rae's mother.

1095
00:58:51,968 --> 00:58:54,604
(Double-peace sign)

1096
00:58:55,072 --> 00:58:56,940
She's seriously so cute.

1097
00:59:01,812 --> 00:59:03,646
Look at you.

1098
00:59:03,647 --> 00:59:04,748
Can I give you a hug?

1099
00:59:05,282 --> 00:59:06,750
Welcome, ma'am.

1100
00:59:08,752 --> 00:59:09,786
Beside Han Gyeol?

1101
00:59:12,089 --> 00:59:13,122
(Stands beside Han Gyeol)

1102
00:59:13,123 --> 00:59:14,658
- She went over there.
- My goodness.

1103
00:59:16,927 --> 00:59:19,563
I can't help but smile like this.

1104
00:59:22,065 --> 00:59:28,872
(However, Han Gyeol
and Eun Na Rae can't seem to smile.)

1105
00:59:29,740 --> 00:59:32,074
They both look very nervous right now.

1106
00:59:32,075 --> 00:59:33,142
I can tell from their expressions.

1107
00:59:33,143 --> 00:59:35,111
This is tough.

1108
00:59:35,112 --> 00:59:36,445
All three of them are nervous.

1109
00:59:36,446 --> 00:59:37,280
The decision?

1110
00:59:38,982 --> 00:59:41,384
(What will
Han Gyeol's mother's decision be?)

1111
00:59:41,385 --> 00:59:42,953
What will Han Gyeol's mother decide on?

1112
00:59:44,488 --> 00:59:45,588
Maybe she won't come.

1113
00:59:45,589 --> 00:59:47,823
- I don't know.
- Maybe she won't come.

1114
00:59:47,824 --> 00:59:48,725
You don't know?

1115
00:59:49,760 --> 00:59:51,093
I'm really not sure.

1116
00:59:51,094 --> 00:59:52,128
Really?

1117
00:59:52,129 --> 00:59:54,097
No, I believe that she'll come.

1118
00:59:57,100 --> 01:00:00,870
I think she was worried from the start.

1119
01:00:00,871 --> 01:00:03,539
The age gap was the biggest concern,

1120
01:00:03,540 --> 01:00:06,909
and I think she was also worried about...

1121
01:00:06,910 --> 01:00:09,612
us getting married
and the things that come after.

1122
01:00:09,613 --> 01:00:12,682
I felt that she was looking for a woman...

1123
01:00:12,683 --> 01:00:15,118
who was very different from me.

1124
01:00:15,786 --> 01:00:20,056
(No one can tell what she's going to do.)

1125
01:00:20,057 --> 01:00:21,825
What do you think?
Do you think she'll come in?

1126
01:00:22,292 --> 01:00:23,959
Just...

1127
01:00:23,960 --> 01:00:24,828
I want her to come in.

1128
01:00:24,829 --> 01:00:26,595
I want her to come in.

1129
01:00:26,596 --> 01:00:28,330
Because it's too...

1130
01:00:28,331 --> 01:00:29,865
- I think she might come in.
- Right?

1131
01:00:29,866 --> 01:00:34,137
I didn't think she would
until a minute ago, but...

1132
01:00:34,871 --> 01:00:36,740
With them...

1133
01:00:37,240 --> 01:00:39,409
I think she will, even though
we think she won't.

1134
01:00:42,212 --> 01:00:47,416
(The wait continues.)

1135
01:00:47,417 --> 01:00:49,286
This is too...

1136
01:00:54,078 --> 01:00:55,279
Maybe she's not coming.

1137
01:01:05,823 --> 01:01:06,923
She's coming.

1138
01:01:06,924 --> 01:01:08,026
See?

1139
01:01:08,393 --> 01:01:10,360
Yes.

1140
01:01:10,361 --> 01:01:12,696
Yes, she's here.

1141
01:01:12,697 --> 01:01:14,231
(Everyone's happy with Han Gyeol's
mother's approval.)

1142
01:01:14,232 --> 01:01:15,933
Congratulations.

1143
01:01:20,505 --> 01:01:22,573
(Stops)

1144
01:01:23,107 --> 01:01:25,342
- You can come in. Come.
- Why isn't she coming?

1145
01:01:25,343 --> 01:01:26,344
Why aren't you coming?

1146
01:01:28,813 --> 01:01:30,848
She couldn't bring herself to walk in.

1147
01:01:32,517 --> 01:01:33,917
Thank you.

1148
01:01:33,918 --> 01:01:35,253
How pretty.

1149
01:01:38,222 --> 01:01:39,424
Thank you.

1150
01:01:43,027 --> 01:01:46,029
I thought maybe you wouldn't come.

1151
01:01:46,030 --> 01:01:46,964
You did?

1152
01:01:46,965 --> 01:01:49,434
Han Gyeol's thoughts are my thoughts.

1153
01:01:50,535 --> 01:01:52,003
Yes, of course.

1154
01:01:53,104 --> 01:01:54,771
You're both wearing similar clothes today.

1155
01:01:54,772 --> 01:01:56,139
Yes, the color.

1156
01:01:56,140 --> 01:01:59,376
Right? I saw earlier
and noticed the brown.

1157
01:01:59,377 --> 01:02:01,745
We have the same vibes.

1158
01:02:01,746 --> 01:02:02,847
Same vibes.

1159
01:02:07,118 --> 01:02:08,086
Eun Na Rae,

1160
01:02:08,586 --> 01:02:12,223
thank you for choosing Han Gyeol.

1161
01:02:14,459 --> 01:02:19,429
There are still things
that I'm concerned about,

1162
01:02:19,430 --> 01:02:24,035
but we will find ways to compromise.

1163
01:02:25,737 --> 01:02:28,238
Na Rae's mother already has a son-in-law.

1164
01:02:28,239 --> 01:02:32,909
Right? I'm glad
the time here wasn't wasted.

1165
01:02:32,910 --> 01:02:34,746
Thank you.

1166
01:02:35,680 --> 01:02:39,182
There you go.
Seo Han Gyeol and Cho Eun Na Rae...

1167
01:02:39,183 --> 01:02:42,085
are officially a final couple.

1168
01:02:42,086 --> 01:02:44,154
- They made it.
- Congratulations.

1169
01:02:44,155 --> 01:02:45,356
It feels so good.

1170
01:02:46,991 --> 01:02:48,459
I'm happy,

1171
01:02:49,160 --> 01:02:51,396
but I'm still nervous.

1172
01:02:51,963 --> 01:02:54,665
My mother also had a hard time here,

1173
01:02:54,666 --> 01:02:56,968
but I think she believed in me.

1174
01:02:58,102 --> 01:03:01,204
I was also so nervous,

1175
01:03:01,205 --> 01:03:05,242
and I want to say how grateful I am.

1176
01:03:05,243 --> 01:03:09,313
I will cherish your thoughts...

1177
01:03:10,248 --> 01:03:15,018
and we'll get to know each other
in a fun and comfortable way.

1178
01:03:15,019 --> 01:03:16,020
Thank you.

1179
01:03:16,954 --> 01:03:22,559
Our five-night, six-day journey
has finally come to an end.

1180
01:03:22,560 --> 01:03:23,528
How do you feel?

1181
01:03:23,529 --> 01:03:27,664
Getting to know someone in six days...

1182
01:03:27,665 --> 01:03:30,434
- isn't something easy.
- Of course.

1183
01:03:30,435 --> 01:03:34,538
I'm happy that we got two couples,

1184
01:03:34,539 --> 01:03:38,108
and from start to finish, it was
a nonstop series of thrills and twists.

1185
01:03:38,109 --> 01:03:41,545
And having the mothers with us...

1186
01:03:41,546 --> 01:03:44,715
was such a fun and interesting twist.

1187
01:03:44,716 --> 01:03:45,650
Right.

1188
01:03:45,651 --> 01:03:48,318
The mothers have approved,

1189
01:03:48,319 --> 01:03:50,253
so if everything's good,
they should just get married.

1190
01:03:50,254 --> 01:03:51,689
Right, exactly.

1191
01:03:52,023 --> 01:03:56,026
Thank you to all the participants,

1192
01:03:56,027 --> 01:03:58,095
and great work, mothers.

1193
01:03:58,096 --> 01:04:00,264
- Thank you.
- Yes, thank you.

1194
01:04:00,832 --> 01:04:03,367
On our show,

1195
01:04:03,368 --> 01:04:07,838
we're looking for those who want
to meet their partners with your parents.

1196
01:04:07,839 --> 01:04:09,473
If you'd like to participate,

1197
01:04:09,474 --> 01:04:14,077
please don’t hesitate
and contact the address on the screen.

1198
01:04:14,078 --> 01:04:17,014
I hope we get to see you again.

1199
01:04:17,015 --> 01:04:18,983
We’ll say goodbye here.

1200
01:04:19,283 --> 01:04:21,019
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

1201
01:04:25,623 --> 01:04:29,393
I think your child gets to know
something about their mother,

1202
01:04:29,394 --> 01:04:33,398
and the mother gets to know
something about their child.

1203
01:04:34,632 --> 01:04:37,100
I didn't know how cheery she was.

1204
01:04:37,101 --> 01:04:38,336
It's dope.

1205
01:04:40,071 --> 01:04:42,306
I got to realize...

1206
01:04:42,807 --> 01:04:44,776
how fun and cheerful she was.

1207
01:04:44,976 --> 01:04:48,578
It was also cute to see...

1208
01:04:48,579 --> 01:04:50,882
how all the mothers
got so close to each other.

1209
01:04:51,783 --> 01:04:55,252
(First time
seeing my mother's cheerful side)

1210
01:04:55,253 --> 01:04:57,154
I always...

1211
01:04:57,155 --> 01:04:58,655
thought that she was a baby,

1212
01:04:58,656 --> 01:05:01,725
but I realized how mature she was
and how I could trust her.

1213
01:05:01,726 --> 01:05:04,094
That's what I thought.

1214
01:05:04,095 --> 01:05:06,596
I knew you'd pick that person.

1215
01:05:06,597 --> 01:05:07,597
Really? you're right.

1216
01:05:07,598 --> 01:05:10,634
I'm happy to know
that we made the same choice.

1217
01:05:10,635 --> 01:05:14,072
I noticed how similar I was to my mom.

1218
01:05:15,006 --> 01:05:17,574
We were both...

1219
01:05:17,575 --> 01:05:21,645
looking and noticing
similar things about guys.

1220
01:05:21,646 --> 01:05:22,580
Cute.

1221
01:05:23,881 --> 01:05:24,716
Cute.

1222
01:05:25,049 --> 01:05:28,353
(Realizing
that we have similar preferences)

1223
01:05:28,686 --> 01:05:30,421
Her eyes seem

1224
01:05:31,055 --> 01:05:32,589
- I don't think so.
- What?

1225
01:05:32,590 --> 01:05:33,624
I don't think so.

1226
01:05:34,659 --> 01:05:36,894
I'm thinking of marriage,

1227
01:05:37,295 --> 01:05:38,963
so it is getting hard for me.

1228
01:05:39,849 --> 01:05:40,717
However,

1229
01:05:41,566 --> 01:05:43,567
to think that there's someone
who's making me think that...

1230
01:05:43,568 --> 01:05:45,103
That itself it meaningful.

1231
01:05:45,503 --> 01:05:48,638
One day, it's like heaven,
then it's like hell.

1232
01:05:48,639 --> 01:05:50,408
Sometimes, I'm full of dopamine,

1233
01:05:50,908 --> 01:05:52,843
but then sometimes,
I feel like I could faint from stress.

1234
01:05:52,844 --> 01:05:54,779
I realized that my feelings
were aligned with my daughter's.

1235
01:05:56,381 --> 01:05:58,782
(Being sad together)

1236
01:05:58,783 --> 01:06:00,218
- Why are you tearing up?
- I'm not crying.

1237
01:06:00,551 --> 01:06:02,185
You've got to eat to cheer up.

1238
01:06:02,186 --> 01:06:03,121
You should cheer up.

1239
01:06:04,255 --> 01:06:08,058
I've lived apart from my mother
for a long time,

1240
01:06:08,059 --> 01:06:10,227
so being able to stay in the same area,

1241
01:06:10,228 --> 01:06:14,631
and being able to share our thoughts
together like this...

1242
01:06:14,632 --> 01:06:16,234
felt very precious.

1243
01:06:17,001 --> 01:06:20,404
I got to make great memories...

1244
01:06:20,405 --> 01:06:23,306
with my child...

1245
01:06:23,307 --> 01:06:26,943
and spend an amazing time
with these great people.

1246
01:06:26,944 --> 01:06:28,546
I'm so thankful for that.

1247
01:06:29,147 --> 01:06:32,215
Whenever Myo Jin went on dates,

1248
01:06:32,216 --> 01:06:34,384
I was getting butterflies.

1249
01:06:34,385 --> 01:06:36,186
I was happy with her.

1250
01:06:36,187 --> 01:06:38,990
(Being happy together)

1251
01:06:39,724 --> 01:06:41,459
Have fun.

1252
01:06:41,793 --> 01:06:43,827
- Thank you.
- Mom.

1253
01:06:43,828 --> 01:06:46,029
(Mothers wished
for their child's happiness.)

1254
01:06:46,030 --> 01:06:48,266
Look at my son blushing
because I said that.

1255
01:06:49,033 --> 01:06:51,602
Bye. Have fun.

1256
01:06:52,904 --> 01:06:54,104
Now,

1257
01:06:54,105 --> 01:06:56,808
I feel like I can step back and watch.

1258
01:06:57,442 --> 01:06:58,776
I have that trust now.

1259
01:07:00,511 --> 01:07:02,013
I trust my son.

1260
01:07:02,580 --> 01:07:05,315
You need to be happy
for me to be happy.

1261
01:07:05,316 --> 01:07:06,818
I love you, Jin Joo.

1262
01:07:07,752 --> 01:07:09,752
Dramaday.me

